::Killfest/Demise::

Killfest turns as he hears Darkmouse's voice. He looks at her. "Yes. 
Things are looking to be turning quickly into a battle. I am here to 
meet Drillbit shortly. You know the base and the troops better than 
me, do you suggest I ally with DrillBit?"

He looks at Demise. Demise nods, recieving orders from Killfest 
through the internal comm, and walks out of the room, heading for the 
bridge.
